\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Where were you born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 9 Bossell Terrace, Buckfastleigh. Oh just - opposite the Town Hall.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How many years did you live in the house where you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well I was there until - October 1933.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 In the one house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How many brothers and sisters did you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Two brothers and two sisters.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Were they older or younger than you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - one sister was older than - I was and - the other three were younger.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How much older was the older one than you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - about two years older.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Were the others very much younger than you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - about two years difference between each of us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How old was your father when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - about - twenty-eight I would say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Where did he come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh he was born in Buckfastleigh.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What did he do for a job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 He was a mercantile clerk. A mercantile clerk, up in the - factory offices.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did he have any job before or after he became a mercantile clerk?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did he ever have any part time jobs as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did he do this all his life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Until he died?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well until - 1921 when the - Hobday Rose Society bought the factory.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What happened then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well he - he left then and - then - did voluntary jobs on his own account.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What kind of jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well, he was the income tax collector at the time he died and - he did a bit of - trade in the woo}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3631648\charrsid7931254 l}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 len you know, blouses and - shirts, that sort of thing on his own account.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Do you remember your father ever being out of work at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No, not - not what you may call out of work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What does that mean?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
Well - there's that period - between the time he left the factory and the - the time he - started on his own, there was a question of - being paid compensation.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was this when the Co-op took over the mill you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was he sort of laid off there or did he want to sort of set out on his own anyway?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh no, he - he was - he was laid off.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How old was your mother when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - about - yes, just a bit younger.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Where did she come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Totnes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Had she any jobs before she got married do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well I - I just don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did she work after she was married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No.
