\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well, I don't - just don't know now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What kind of people would they be, were they shopkeepers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - difficult to say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was your father ever a member of anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You say when you were at school you always came home for your midday meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How did you feel about your teachers, did you get on fine with your teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh we used to get on with 'em all right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You didn't feel they weren't teaching you anything or anything like that, did you sort of feel that you were getting a lot out of school?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh yes, I think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did they ever teach you things like what you were going to do when you left school, did they give you any practical -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 If you did anything that the teachers disapproved of what would happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
Oh - well I remember one incident - at the school - involved the lady teacher that was in the boys school. And some of the lads, they set about her one - one evening and - they - I think the
y were severely punished for it, but - what it was I don't know. What sort of punishment they had I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you ever see the teacher carry a stick or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh the - schoolmaster always used to carry a cane.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did he ever use it in the classroom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Sometimes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You don't remember ever having the stick yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would girls get the same punishment as the boys?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 They'd be in a different section wouldn't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes. I don't - just can't tell you about the boys school nor - nor the infants.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did your parents show an interest in your school work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well I think they did but - difficult to say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you ever have school reports or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did they ever go to the school to see the teachers or did any of the teacher ever come to your home to talk to them about you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No, not to my knowledge.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did they ever ask you what you did at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well it's difficult to say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did the other children come from the same kind of home as you? Where would all the other children come from would they be local boys?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh mostly local I think. But in late years, when - Dean school and - Combe school they all came in here. That was after my time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Were there any gangs or groups in the school can you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
Oh I don't think so, the - they weren't - well what shall I say, weren't over - bad. But when you speak of gangs. Not - not like you get today anyhow.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Do you remember any children at school who were left out of things at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No, I don't remember that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you go on to any other school afterwards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No. But - I sat for an examination for - for to go Ashford grammar school but I didn't pass.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How old were you when you sat for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - about seven or eight I think.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What kind of things would you have to do? Was it sort of like an eleven plus now?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well can be - that doesn't worry about eleven plus you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 It was sort of sums and essays and things like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes, and drawing and - got to draw sort of things and - you -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was it Ashburton grammar school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Ashburton grammar school it was, yes. By Templar station there. Well next door to the po - bit further than the police station.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would that have been fee paying?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - oh scholarship I believe.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How old were you when you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Fourteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you ever attend any part time education afterwards? Any evening classes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you ever have any regrets about your education, would you have liked to have bone on to Ashburton grammar school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - might have been to my advantage.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Whose idea was it that you took the exam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 My - my parents, they wanted me to go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did they sort of put you in for it, or did the teacher say anything about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - oh they-- they spoke to my teacher about it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3631648\charrsid7931254 Do you think you benefi}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 ted from attending school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh I think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 In what way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - well difficult to say what way but - of course I sort of - improved my knowledge as - time went on.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 While you were at school or after you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well after I left school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did the teacher ever allow you to bring books home or anything like that, or did you do 
everything inside school, did you have any homework or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 I believe we used to have homework. But I'm not quite sure now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did the teachers expect you to be there on time at school, what happened if you were late for school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well that's - difficult to remember now. But you - we had to be there on time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was there a school bell and things like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh yes, school bell.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What would you eat, what kind of things would you drink with meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh used to have tea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did your mother ever make anything like home made wine or brew beer or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did she make her own bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No, we used to buy our bread.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What about jam, did she ever make her own jam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh she may have made a little. It's difficult to remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you have a garden where you lived?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Only a small one but - father used to have an allotment.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What would he grow there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well grow - potatoes, peas and beans.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would that keep you in supply of vegetables for the year or would you have to buy vegetables on top of that?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh we might have had to buy - in the off season.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you ever keep anything like livestock, pigs or hens?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh he kept hens, for a time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would they be on the allotment?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you ever have chicken to eat from these fowls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh I believe we had some. This is after - oh well after - after - after 1918.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 But you had the allotment before 1918 did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes, I think so. Yes, he just - he must have done 'cos - used to be up in - Bossel Lane, up - near Bossel House.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Whereabouts is that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
Well up - it's up past the Town Hall. Up past the school. Used to go up over the hill and then down a lane on the left just the other side of Bossel House.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Who would look after the hens, would they be all right on their own during the day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would your mother ever make things like bottled fruit or bottled vegetables, pickles or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh it's difficult to remember - remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you have any fruit trees or anything like that on the allotment?
