\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well, it's difficult to say. Might have been - three or four times a week. Difficult to remember, it's so long ago.
