\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How about mushrooming?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes, I think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What time of day would you have to get up for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - early in the morning. Have to go before breakfast really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was that quite regular or just now and again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh just now and again.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Do you ever remember seeing your mother having less food so that the rest of you could have more to eat?
