\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Do you ever remember seeing your father eat more? Having more to eat than anyone else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Were you allowed to talk during meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh yes. I think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Could you choose what you wanted to eat from what was cooked or did you have to have a bit of everything?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh we had - we had to have what was going.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What was your parents attitude if you left some food uneaten on the plate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well there's -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would they say anything to you about it or would they make you eat it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well they wouldn't - they wouldn't force us to eat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
If there was something on the table you wanted like the salt could you just get it or did you have to have it passed, or wait for it to be passed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh just - we would just ask for it if we wanted it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 There were no sort of tight rules about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No. Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Could you ask for a second helping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes, I think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Were you expected to hold your knife and fork in a certain way and eat in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh just the - normal way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Could you bring toys or a book to the table in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was that because your parents would disapprove?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well I think they liked us - reading or any - during meals.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Could you leave the table at any time or did you have to ask?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well we usually - we usually - used to ask.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You didn't have to wait 'til the end of the meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did all the family sit at the table for the meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes, as far as I can remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you have the same positions every time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 I believe - I believe we did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Where would your father sit? Was he at the he}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3631648\charrsid7931254 a}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 d of the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - was a round table we had, where - we've still got it now. Oh he used - his - sort of position if I remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Who would do the carving?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - he - he did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes. He'd do the carving.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Where would your mother serve the meal, would she bring it to the table or would she bring it from the stove?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh she'd serve it from the table I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Where would your younger brothers and sisters sit before they could feed themselves? Would they be at the table as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well I don't remember that one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Who would feed them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well that - that I don't remember. I expect mother did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was your mother a very easy person to talk to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well I think so. She's very - rather a stout person you know, big built person.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you get on OK with her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh we got on all right, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 If you had any worries would you be able to share them with her?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well that's - that's difficult to answer now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Do you remember having any sort of scrapes you got into and you had to sort of ask her to bail you out or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No, I don't - I just don't remember that now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was your father the same? Did you get on OK with your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was he easy to talk to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh yes, I think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How did your parents expect you to behave towards them do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - I don't think they let us take any liberties. They was - we always address 'e
m as - mum or dad or mother and father, whatever the case might be.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Do you think they were very strict with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh they were - yes they were - strict if anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What do you think they tried to make you think were the important things in life? What kind of values did they expect to grow up to respect?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - I just don't remember now. Of course we - I will say one thing, we had a good upbringing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did they bring you up to believe in religion?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh yes. Of course they were devou
t church people of course - you'd have to go to Sunday school every - Sunday morn - Sunday - morning, afternoon go to church. Yes, they were rather strict about that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did they go along with you to the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Father used to mornings and - father and mother evening.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would you ever bring anybody back to the house after church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - we used to have a - bring in a friend or two, after church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What would you do then?
