\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did your parents bring you up to behave towards your brothers and sisters in any particular way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh yes, I think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well I mean they - they wouldn't - they wouldn't let us fight one another or anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did they ask you to look after yo
ur younger brothers and sisters? Sort of keep an eye on them, if they went out or you went out with them, did they expect you to look after them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh I think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What did they think of swearing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Not very much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 If you did something that your parents disapproved of what would happen?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well, I was going to say - going to say we - severely reprimand us you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What would that involve?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - well give us - give us a good talking to. It - I don't suppose - I don't think it went any fur - would go any further than that.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did they sort of send you to your room or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would you ever get punished other than verbally? Would it ever be anything more than just being told off?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 W
ould you say that you received your ideas about how to behave from both your parents, or was one more influential than the other? Who do you think taught you most?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well I - I was going to say - father was the more - more in - influential, but - of the two.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was he sort of master of the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh yes, I - I would definitely say that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Were there any occasions when he'd tell you off and your mother would say don't be too hard on them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What would happen if you had a birthday, would it be different from any other day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No. I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would you have any birthday cards or presents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh yes. Get birthday cards.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would you bring friends round for a party or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No, not - I don't think so. Difficult to remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you have anything special to eat on your birthday?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well that's difficult to say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You can't remember any special birthday present or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you have presents as well as cards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh yes, we may have had a present.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What kind of things would you get?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - it's difficult to say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would you get some sweets?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Perhaps - might get - hankies or something like that. Small and useful.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Who would give you the presents, your friends or would it be your parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well that's difficult to say really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Can you remember anything that you did with your mother and father on Christmas Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 I'm afraid I can't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You say you didn't have any musical instruments in the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Not at that time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would anybody sing in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
Well, as far as I - re - remember - in the days before the first war - my father had a brother - working in the factory, he - he lived - lived in the Town Hall you know, 
he was curator at the Town Hall. Well they used to come over - spend Christmas Day with us, we used to go over and spend New Year's day with them. That's the arrangement we always used to have when we were younger.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What kind of things would happen, would you have a big meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - yes, a good meal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would you go to Church on Christmas Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would you play games or anything like that on Christmas Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well, we may have done. Played games or perhaps played cards.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What about things like playing cards on a Sunday, what would your parents think of that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well that's difficult to say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 They didn't sort of tell you not to play cards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did your parents ever play any games with you? In the house or outside the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well that's difficult to remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Were there any books in the house, you say you had these books from Sunday school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What about your parents, did they have many books?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 They may have had som
e. I believe in - years and years ago the Co-operative Society used to run the library. I remember going in there sometimes, get a book. That's as far as I can - remember now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did your parents have any books or newspapers or magazines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - oh newspapers yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What newspapers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - used to be a paper called the Western Daily Mercury, printed in Plymouth. And - what was the other one, a London paper?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was that delivered every day, the London paper or was it a weekly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh it's a 
daily paper. I don't think it was News of - Daily News and Chronicle. I really - I can't - can't think of the name of it now, it was a London paper.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 It wasn't the News Chronicle or the Despatch or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh no, we always used to get it from the - newspaper shop. Tit-Bits, we've had Tit-Bits for years and years, and I still have it now.

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Do you remember your mother or father ever reading? To each other or aloud to you as children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No, I don't remember that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Do you ever remember anything like a funeral in the family? Before the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No. Although - there was a child between me and my elder sister that died very young.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 But you were too young to remember that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes, too young to remember it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 So the child would die before you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh after I was born but - I just don't know what happened.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Were you ever taken out visiting neighbours or relatives?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - yes. My father used to have a - sister living down Paignton, no, he had two siste
rs living in Paignton. The husband of one of these sister's used to be manage of the Co-operative Society there. I used to go down there sometimes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You'd have to go all the way over to Paignton?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 All the way to Paignton, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How would you get to Paignton?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh used to - you could get in by train in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How often would you go there, at weekends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Used to go there in the weekends.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Who would go with you, your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 All of us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 The whole family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 My fa
ther went down there one weekend. And I went down alone one weekend I believe and - well go down and back for half a crown for a weekend ticket. From here.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you have any relatives living close by?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2377889\charrsid7931254 Oh just - oh, T}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 otnes, on mother's side.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you ever go and see them very often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh sometimes used to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would they come over and see you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well they used to but they don't come this way very much now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 I mean in the days before the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Do you think your parents would see relatives rather than neighbours in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Or was it a bit of both?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well I - used - I think they used to - didn't used to mind a bit of both.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did they neighbours come in very often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Were you allowed to play with the neighbours children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh yes, we - quite a few of us - quite a few children there - when we were in Bossel Terrace.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What kind of things would you do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - goodness knows.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you play football or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh no, no, we didn't used to play football. We used to - books and drawing perhaps and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you ever go for very many long walks?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 YES? I - I used to when I - after I started work.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 In the time you were at school did you go for walks very often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well I - I don't quite remember that not now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Were you ever taken shopping? Go to Newton Abbott or something to get shopping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No. I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you ever go out with just your father? Or was it mainly together with your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh used to go out - with father more - more than mother if anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was this to go and see relatives?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Or just go for a walk.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What about things like races and things like that, did you ever go there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
Oh we - we used to. Oh yes - that brings another point. My father used to go the - the races every year and - taking money in the grandstand. I used to go up there very often.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 So you were in a nice area?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 That was once every year?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Once every year then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Do you remember anything like fairs or circuses coming?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
Oh yes - always used to - get that sort of thing here. Do you know where - Plymouth Park houses are, that's - next up to the Town Hall, opposite the school. Well that used to be the fair ground.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How often would the fair come?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - difficult to say now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Two or three times a year?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Three - three or two times a year I would say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would you go every time it came?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What kind of things would they have at the fair?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
Oh - roundabouts, swing boats and - hoop-la. And - sweet stalls. And - and they used to have a - used to have a sort of a firing green, you never seen this, you got a - used to have a - shooting - or a shootin
g range that's what I should call it. You - you'd have some and you'd have to - try and fire the balls being pulled up there with water. Shooting range.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did they have prizes and things like that at fairs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 If you shot these things down?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh another thing used to have there on - on the left side of the - firing range was a - a bull}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2377889\charrsid7931254 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2377889\charrsid7931254 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 eye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Like a dartboard bull}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2377889\charrsid7931254 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2377889\charrsid7931254 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 eye?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You know what a bull}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2377889\charrsid7931254 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2377889\charrsid7931254 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 eye is - were plenty of - people try and fire at it. A big card with several rings on it, bull}
{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2377889\charrsid7931254 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2377889\charrsid7931254 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 eye ring in the middle.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you go with your parents to the fair?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No, just us go on our own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did your parents not mind you going to fairs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh not at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you ever have things like village concerts, was there anything like that here?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh I think concerts - used to have 'em at the Town Hall.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How often would they have a concert?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - oh difficult to say. One - one - one crowd used to come here a - a lot in those days was - party called the Walford Fa
mily. Walford. Walford. Walford. Walford. They used to be - come here quite a bit - in the old days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What kind of stuff would they do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well it was - oh pictures for a start and - variety entertainment.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Acrobats and things like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well, no, no acrobats. No acrobatic feats.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did they have sort of singing? Did they ever do things like theatre productions and little acts and things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well I - I forget now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What did the Walfords do particularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - difficult to s
ay, it's - so long ago. Know one of these chaps he had - had a false leg you know, he - he limped a bit. He was a bit of a character.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Where did the Walfords come from, was it a local group?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh no, they come from away somewhere.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did they ever have things like a cinema in Buckfastleigh in those days can you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
Well not a real cinema but they used to run a cinema down the - the old Assembly Rooms down near the Kings Arms. That - used to be run by - somebody from Totnes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What kind of things would they show there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh, the silent pictures.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 They'd be ones that were on general release?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 They'd be moving pictures?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh moving pic - movies, yes, but silent.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Can you remember going on any other outings with your parents, like you went to Paignton, did you ever go on sort of day trips anywhere?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - well yes, we used to go - Sunday school children used to go to Teignmouth every year on a special train. Mother always used to go.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What would you do there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Seaside town, yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would you have to pay to go on that or was that part of the Sunday school treat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh that's part of the Sunday school treat, and the pay church used to pay for that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Were you a member of the choir at church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No. No, I wasn't ever a choir - I was a bell ringer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You were a bell ringer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes. I learned to ring up here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would you ever go on choir outings as a bell}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2377889\charrsid7931254 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 ringer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No. No, I - never remember going to a choir outing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Can you remember things like Bank Holidays, did they have Bank Holidays in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you go anywhere with your parents on Bank Holidays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - see there used to be Easter Monday, well, Good Friday, Easter Monday, Whit Monday and A
ugust Bank Holiday. But every - August Bank Holiday most of the people - used to go up on the moors for the day picnicking. To Wallaford Down -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would you go up there with your parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh yes. Oh parents used to go sometimes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 That would last the whole day would it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Last the whole day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Can you remember ever going away for holidays in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Where did you go to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Where, let me think. 1912 I think was the first I remember. I had a week's holiday here at home
, on me own. 1913 we all went to Teignmouth for a week. And again in 1914, we went Teighmouth for a week.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 This was all your brothers and sisters and your parents.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes, all of us. 1915 we went Torquay. Of course, that - beginning of 1916 - 16 I - went away from home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 This was in the summer was it, the holiday time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes. I think it was about August time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How many week's in the year would your dad have for a holiday? Apart from Bank Holidays and this week would he have any others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - about a week I think, used to have a week's holiday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was this the week you went away?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
Yes. Oh - another thing I - I remember now. Back in 19 - yes, 1904. My - my father's younger sister was living - here in the town then, her husband w
as manager of the Co-op, they - take a house down - Preston Paignton for a month. We were down there for a month.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What year was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh 1904. August.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 They were there for a month, or you went to visit them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh there - we was all there for a month.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would your father be working still during that month?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh yes, he - he used to come - come up and down you know every - every night. Every day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 When you went on the week's holiday to Torqyay and Teignmouth you all went together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you stay in a hotel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No, we - stayed in a - private house you know and - people that used to advertise.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 A guest house type of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well not exactly a guest house. Do you know Torquay at all? Well do you know where B
elgrave Road is? Well down - we stayed down there when we went to Torquay. One of those houses down there, Belgrave Road.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was it coming in then in those days, this idea of having a week's holiday by the seaside? Did most people go off for a holiday o
f some kind in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well I think they did, yes. Or -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you ever have anything like Wakes down here?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - I don't remember that at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Or something like a trades fair?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - no. Not - not here. I've always - we've always used to hear they tell us of goose fair.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You have heard of it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh yes, heard of goose fair, had - had that in Tavistock every year.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you ever go to that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No. Well then there's Widdicome fair, I've been out there once. Widecombe fair.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2377889\charrsid7931254 What happened}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254  at Widecombe fair?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - oh it's a proper - proper to do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was it the same as the fair they had at Buckfastleigh?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh yes, all sorts and - roundabouts and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What time of year would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - September.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would that be a whole day trip out there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Whole day, yes. Well then the - they have - they have a horse sports and all that sort of thing. Jumping and - whatnot. Something -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Like a gymkhana really?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes. Like a gymkhana.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did they have anything like fox hunting or blood sports round here?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well fox hunting yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you ever take part in that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well I've - I've been several times. Of course we got two - two hunts round here. Town Hall Fox hunt and the Dog and Harriers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What time of the year would they meet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh there's third in September, they finish about March.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Could you tell me how you spent Saturdays in those days when you were still at school? What would you do on Saturday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh well that's - that's difficult to say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did anything special happen on Saturday? Would you be taken anywhere perhaps?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No. I just - just don't remember, not now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How about Sundays, what would you do on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh Sundays - Sunday school in the morning, 
ten o'clock. Church eleven o'clock. Sunday school afternoon at - three o'clock I think. And then church Sunday evening.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 It was church and not the chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Church, yes, Church of England.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you have special different clothes on a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes, well - what we called best clothes like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you play games on Saturdays or Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 I don't think so. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did your parents think it was wrong to work or play on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 I don't think they liked it very well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 They didn't play or do anything themselves in the way of work on Sundays?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Your parents were Church of England as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Church of England.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How often would they go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - father and the rest of us used to go Sunday mornings and then mother used to go Sunday evenings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You say you used to go on a Sunday school outing to Teignmouth?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Teighmouth, well that's these - annual Sunday school outing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 That's once a year?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Once a year, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How would you travel, on a train?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Train, yes, used to have our special train.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How many people would go on that? Would parents go as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - yes. Perhaps about - four or five hundred.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 As many as that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would it be all Sunday schools in the neighbourhood, would it be from different villages around?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh no, just Buckfastleigh itself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Five hundred from Buckfastleigh alone?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well then the other denominations used to have their own you know. The Wesleyans and the Congregationals, they used to
 have their own outing as well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 So the five hundred were all Church of England Sunday school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 They were - yes, connected with the - Church of England.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did they all turn up at the Sunday school at the same time, the five hundred?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh well - that includes a lot of parents.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Were there any other social activities organised by the church that you took part in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - one thing I could - I can think of, the - church choir used to have a - annual outing every - every year. Used to be on Saturday.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 That was separate from the Sunday school outing was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You say you weren't a member of this church choir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 When did you start bell ringing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 1911.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you do it at the church or was that just rehearsals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - at the church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 So did that qualify you for anything, was there any social activity attached to bell}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2377889\charrsid7931254 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 ringing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No, not in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What made you take up bell}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2377889\charrsid7931254 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 ringing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well, I don't know. Of course at th
at time - we had a - new vicar in 1908. He came and he - he did a lot of restoration work. And - one of the things he had done was to re}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2377889\charrsid7931254 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 hang the bells. That was about 1911, that's when I learnt.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You've done it ever since?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 YES. Then when I went to - Taunton in 1916 - I was able to take up campanology. Well that's the science of bell}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2377889\charrsid7931254  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 ringing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Are there books and things on it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You continued to bell ring in Taunton did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What church was it there, Church of England again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh yes, was - several churches in Taunton, Church of England.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Where did you live when you went to live in Taunton? Did you have lodgings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh lodgings, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did the church run any temperance club do you remember in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No, but - used to run a Band of Hope. What they call a Band of Hope. Well the Wesleyan used to run that as well, Band of Hope.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - oh I forget now. The sort of thing to - impress a young people connected with churches and chapels.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What was its main thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well I - I -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was a youth club or what?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well really forget now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Were you a member of this Band of Hope?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was, I used to go - to Wesleyans - Band of Hope on - once upon a time, well then when the church started I went to the church one as well.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 When did the church one start then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Before the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Before the first world - world war.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was it against drink for instance?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh it might have been.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Do you remember whether there was much drinking done in Buckfastleigh in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was it just about the same as it is today?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh about the same as it is today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 I was told that it was quite rough at times on Saturday night down town.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Mm. Yes, it might have been. He - he might know - know more about that than I do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was grace said at meals in your family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Pardon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was grace said at meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Were you taught to say prayers at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Who taught you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - our parents.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Both your parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 YES.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you ever have family prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did your father take an interest in politics at all at this time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes. Well we - our political views are Liberal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was he a member of any Liberal organisation?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
Well - I don't think there was any - organisation in those - in those days, except there might have been a - oh yes there was - Liberal Association. Buckfastleigh Liberal Association, of course the 
Conservatives - got it as well. Then the Labour people were - got it now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 In those days it was the Conservatives and the Liberals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes, in the old days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What was the difference between the two do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did your father ever talk about politics or things to do with political attitudes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh he - probably did talk a lot about it but - I just don't - remember just the conversations now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You don't remember any particular instances, how did he feel about being laid 
off for instance when the Co-op took over, did he say anything about that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well, I just - just don't remember really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Why do you think he was a Liberal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well he was a - well very strong - Liberal views.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did he take part in any activity in between general elections, did he do any canvassing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well, I - I don't remember that, not now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You don't remember any sort of political meetings he used to go to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No, not now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What about your mother, what was she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh she was - Liberal as well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Why was that, because your father was or because she had Liberal opinions as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh I think she had Liberal opinions as well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Do you remember your father or mother voting in a general election before 1918?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh yes - they both voted in - general elections, as far as I know of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 And they'd vote Liberal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 In some places there's talk that some men felt they risked losing their jobs if they had a different political vote to their employers.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Mm. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Do you remember anything like that happening in Buckfastleigh around that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No, I don't remember anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What about your father, were the Hamblyns Liberal or Conservative?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh they were Conservatives. Buckfastleigh itself was a really a - Liberal stronghold. Mm. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Do you remember your father feeling under any pressure to vote Conservative, through the Hamblyns being Conservative?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 He was able to do what he wanted?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 He was - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 When your parents were not at work how did they spend their time? What kind of things would they do to pass the time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - I can't say so much about mother but - father used to go over to the Town Hall you know and - when the Town Hall was run by truste
es, go and have a game of bowls or a game of cards. And then Saturday nights he - used to slip out and have a quiet drink. The Golden Lion was open then, that's - right opposite the factory.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How often would he go down to the Town Hall, would that be during weeknights?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh some week nights.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would your mother ever go out with him on these occasions?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well I just don't remember, not now.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 But she might have stayed at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did your mother ever have any interests outside of the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - yes, she was - she was a member of the Church of England Mothers Union.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How often would they meet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - well say every so often. Perhaps once a month, perhaps - perhaps more or less.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What kind of activities did they do, did they have whist drives or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well they had some sort of - social evening you know, perhaps a meeting with a special speaker.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did they have sort of garden fetes in this area at that time, church garden fetes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 I believe so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Do you remember anything of garden fetes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
There's only one I might possibly remember, but that was up at Harewood, that's up - past the school. It's a - big house turned into flats now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What kind of things would they have there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - I just don't remember - I'm afraid.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was it a summer fete or winter fete?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh summer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did your mother ever help with any organising any stalls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 She might have done.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was she a very active member?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well then - before the war, the church used to have bazaars, she used to take an interest in that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did people come round from the mother's union to discuss things or to organise things or did she go down to the Mothers Union?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - she might have - gone to some meetings or - somebody might have called to see her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Where did they meet, the Mothers Union? Was that the Town Hall as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No - do you remember during - up opposite the factory, well next door to the Co-operative stores, that used to be a chur
ch Sunday school. They used to meet in there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What time did your father get home from work in the evenings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well I'm not sure whether it was - five o'clock or six o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How many evenings a week would he stay at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well that - that depends what - what was doing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 There wasn't a sort of regular routine of one night out and the rest in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No. Just a matter of what was doing at the time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You say your father attended the Town Hall, was he a member of any club as such? You
 say he was president of the Co-operative Wholesale Society?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well he was a - he was a member of the Town Hall.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did he ever take part in council work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh yes, he - oh he was clerk to the Buckfastleigh West Parish Council as I said yesterday
, but - he wasn't 'til 1925 he got on the local council.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What did he do on that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - you know, counci}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2377889\charrsid7931254 l}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 lor. Well then of course he - he was on until - nearly 1930 well then he - he passed on them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How often would he go down if he was president of the Co-op, was he president of the Co-op before the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How often would he have to attend meetings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - once a week. I believe it was Tuesdays.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would he sort of have to present information and things like that? What did a president of the Co-op have to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
Well - he'd have to take the chair at the committee meetings and - and perhaps - I think he used to take a chair at the - quarterly meetings. As far as I can remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You say your father was a treasurer up at the race course?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
No, he wasn't treasurer, he used to take - money inside the - inside the grandstand. See, they had - they had two entrances, say here's the grandstand, here's the - gallery and that here like, well there was a - ther
e's a box there, you know, a - there's an entry with a box there and a - entry with a box this side. So there used to be one each side. My father used to be this side if I - remember rightly. Facing - Dean church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What kind of people would be in the g
randstand? How much did it cost to get into the grandstand in those days? Was it the same as standing or did they have to pay a bit more for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well I think you had to pay a bit more.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did most people go into the sort of ordinary stand up positions? Did the Hamblyns and people like that go to the races?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 I believe so. All the - most of - see all the - what I call the nobility, all these better class people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did he ever bet on these races?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Not very often. I remember him doing it once. That's about all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did he ever win on it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well this particular horse was second I believe which he did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was he a member of any savings club at the time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh yes, he - he took an interest in that. During the war. Savings clubs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What about boot or sick societies, was he anything to do with that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Anything to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 A boot society? Sort of where you put money in, a sort of investment?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was he a member of any sick society or any insurance, things like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
Oh yes, he was - he was chairman of one of the friendly societies for several years. Then in 1923 when the - secretary died he took over the secretary-ship, until he - until he died. But -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 So he had an awful lot of things on his plate really?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did he have anything like where you put money in to pay towards a funeral?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
Well - I don't remember anything about that, the only thing - the only thing I can re - remember was - his friendly society and - used to pay into one of the - provident societies, I believe it was the - him, can't think of the name now - Prudential.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was that common in those days do you think to pay money into these?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 I believe so. I believe it was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How did you get on with your brothers and sisters while you were still at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh sometimes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was there any one brother or sister you felt particularly close to at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - my eldest sister I think was the one that - I got on the best of all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How old was she when she went to London to work and live?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - soon after she left school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Who would you play with more when you were young, would you play with your brothers or sisters or would it be neighbours more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh we used to play with - we used to play together with - some of the neighbours children, some of us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What kind of things would you play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh all the -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Anything like hoops, hula hoop sticks or tops or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well might have played marbles but - I just can't - remember now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Where would you play, would there be a back yard or garden?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - well we used to play in the front.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you ever go into other people's homes to play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Not very often.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you play in the garden at all or weren\rquote t you allowed to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No, not - no garden in the back but a garden in the front, used to play in the front.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you ever grow vegetables in the front garden or was that all on the allotment?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh no, that's - that was all on the allotment.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What would be in the front garden then, just grass?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh grass and - flowers and that, rose bushes and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Were you allowed to get dirty when you played?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - I don't think so. We had to wash when we did so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Were you free to play with anyone you liked to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 There wasn't anybody your mother said she didn't want to play with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 There weren't any rough children around?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Weren't any rough children round where we were living then. Not what you call rough children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you belong to any youth organisations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No, there - there wasn't any at that time?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What about the Band of Hope?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh well that's - Band of Hope, yes, we used to go Band of Hope now and again.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What about the YMCA, was that there then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
Well I was - that was there then but I wasn't a member of that then. Well then - just before the war they used to have - the church used to run a troupe of boy scouts but - I wasn't - anything to do with that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Were there many of your friends in the boys scouts?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you ever have any hobbies at this time do you remember? I suppose bell ringing would be a hobby wouldn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes, it would be.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Anything else you can think of?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well, that's about all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you ever collect things like eggs or stamps or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you have any pets in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No, no pets.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you ever go fishing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No, never used to go fishing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What about bike rides, did you have a bike?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Not until - not until I went away from home, I - I learnt to - I learnt to ride a bike when I was in Taunton.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you buy it yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well then when I came home I - I don't remember whether I bought one or not but I - I had a - I had a bicycle when I -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 After 1919 when you came home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you ever take part in any sports at all, you say you went to the races?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 I've got some recollection of - taking part in - one or two - sports meetings, that's about all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What kind of things would happen then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh well sports you know - I believe the - friendly society used to run that sort of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would it be sort of athletics or would it be football or rugby or cricket?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh no, just -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What about things like sick races and egg and spoon races, did they have that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well they used to years ago, but I just don't - can't remember when you know. They might have had a lot while I was away from home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You say there was the Walfords and the concert and the cinema down near the Kings Arms? Did your parents ever give you any pocket money?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes, I believe - they did give a - yes, when - when we started earning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How much did they give you roughly? This is before you went to work or after?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh after I went to work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 So you wouldn't get any pocket money when you were still at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 When you were working did you give your mother the money that you earned?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 And then she gave you some pocket money out of it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Give me a little pocket money, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was this a regular thing, did you get it every week?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 I think so, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What kind of things did you spend the money on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh goodness knows in those days. We might have bought a few sweets for ourselves. And of course - keep a little for Sunday collection.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you ever go for very long walks or walks anywhere?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well we used to - crowd of us used to go - go out for walks Sunday afternoons, crowd of us - together you know. Me an
d my - second brother and later my younger brother and - quite a few other young chaps.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Where would you go to? Just round the neighbourhood?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes. A favourite walk was down - down around what they call the Bridges you know where the weir is, well down round - down round that way.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What time would you have to be back from these walks?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh about tea time. Well then -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did your parents ever go for walks with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No. Then just before I went to Taunton - after Sunday school I always
 used to go up Totnes Road for a walk. Went up Weston Hill and back again.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 There's so many lovely walks all round here aren't there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes. Well it's on - it's only been in late years that I've - got a - got about a great deal more.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 I suppose in those times when you were working you wouldn't have an awful lot of spare time to go for walks anyway would you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No. No. Well I always remember - when I was working in the paper mill - about this time of the year, when I'd finished work in the ev
ening I used to go out - picking violets. Just round - down around Totnes Road.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Somebody was telling me that all she wild flowers are being lifted by people, tourists?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes, yes, they - they are. Unfortunately.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Were there a lot more flowers in those days growing wild?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you ever do things like press flowers in books, collect flowers or leave and things and press them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Do you remember anyone outside of the home helping your mother run the family at all? Or look after the house, anyone come in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - yes, there was - one or two - I could think of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Who would they be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - used to be somebody called Gaynor up Pinehill Terrace, that was one - person and then there's another person called - well do
n't know whether she used to be a midwife or not, she was called - Britters, Nurse Britters.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What would they do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well just come and - keep an eye on us and - but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Where would your mother be while this was happening? Would she be in the house as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
Yes, but she was - she wasn't away - went away to London, oh - about 1911 or 12, 1911 I believe. So this Nurse Britters came down and - gave an eye to us while she was away.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did it just happen that once or did it happen a few times?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Only that once I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did they sort of live in while your mother was away?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 I don't think so. I don't think she'd live in, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How often did you have relations round? Would Totnes be a long way away in those days for your mother's re
lations to come? Or would it be quite easy to get to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
Well - used to be able to get there by train. Well then - well we used - I think we - used to go in there now and again before the war and - they used to come out. Then mother had a sister in 
London, they used to come there about - once or twice a year to see us.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would you ever go up to London to see them as children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh yes. Well not - not as children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 When was the first time you went up to London?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 1920. I was working in the Midlands then, I came home - for a few days and then - I spent the rest of the time in London.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What about your father's relatives, they were from Buckfastleigh were they, your father's people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Originally I believe.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Were there many of them around when you were young?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh it's difficult to say now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Whose relatives would be most frequently there, your mother's or your father's?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh my mother's side mostly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What would happen if your mother was ill or confined to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well, I just don't remember now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You don't remember anything like that ever?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Can you remember anything about when one of your brothers or sisters was born? Were you able to remember anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - the only thing I can
 re - sort of - got any recollection of was when my youngest - brother was born. He was born on King Edward's coronation day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was that 1903?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 1902. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was he supposed to be lucky because of that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well I don't know. But - I remember I 
was up in - mother's bedroom in the evening and there was a big bonfire up here, I remember looking at the bonfire.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you have its of people in on Coronation Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - I don't remember, not - so far back as that. Oh - but the - it was wet C
oronation Day, that's King George the Fifth. I remember it raining that day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did Royalty ever come down this part of the world?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well they used to I believe.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would you have a day off when that happened? A sort of a national holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - I really don't remember now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did your parents have many friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well I think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
Would your father's committee members and groups of the friendly society, would they ever come back to the house and have a drink or something?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well that - that I don't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You don't remember sort of hordes of people in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did your mother and father share the same friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes. I think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did your mother have any friends of her own, that were her own friends rather than your father's?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well that I'm not quite clear on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did she sort of have - if she was at home and your father was at work she'd know more about the neighbours than your father perhaps?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes. Well - well talking about that, she might go in and - see the neighbours or the neighbours might come in and see her about anything.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did they ever do jobs for each other, errands and things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 They may have done.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You say your father used to go down to the meetings down at 
the Town Hall and the Co-op and friendly society, odds and ends like that, so that's where he'd meet most of his friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Or down the pub on Saturday night? Would friends be invited into the home or would they just come along as the fancy took them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh as the fancy took them I would say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would they be offered anything to eat or drink?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Not to my knowledge. Well they - might have been asked if they'd like a drink.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would there be any particular occasion when people would come?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 It wouldn't be something like Christmas Day or Boxing Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would you say that the friends who came in were your mother's or your father's friends or would they be both of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - both in a way I would say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You say friends called in casually without an invitation, and the neighbours too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would your parents ever go out to visit friends or neighbours very often, and leave you behind say in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well that's - difficult to say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
People often tell us that in those days they made their own amusements, what do you remember of your parents, how they made their amusements? Would it be mainly things like your father going down to the various committee meet
ings, and your mother with the Mothers Union, would they do anything outside of that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well that's - that's difficult to say now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You can't remember them having sort of social evenings together?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 They wouldn't do anything in the way of music?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well another thing - we had a - talking about going out, they might - used to go to pictures somewhere now and again.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 That was the one next to the Kings Arms?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 I've been in one down there but I'm - not sure whether they didn't used to go to the one that used to be over Station Road.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Where's that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - where the car park is now I think, it's been pulled down.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 There's a cinema there now is there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 There was a cinema there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 So Buckfastleigh had two cinemas in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
Well, only one, because the - one in Kings Arms well that finished - just round - the end of the war I would say. I remember being opened in - when it - being opened in 1915, it was open then but - well when it shut I don't remember now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
People say that society was divided into different social classes in that time. Did you think of some people belonging to one class or group and some to another before 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - oh I don't know really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What would you think the different groups were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
Well the only - thing I can think of was - talking about politics I'll say or somebody belonging to the - Conservative Association others belonging to the Liberal Association, that's what I think. That's the only - answer I can give there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
What class or group would you say you belonged to yourself? You say your family were Liberals? Who would the nobility be, you used the word nobility a while back, who would belong to the nobility?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - well what - what I meant by that th
e - the better class people well like - like the Hamlyns or - or shall I put it this way, people - people with means.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Who would that include apart from the sort of mill owners? Was that church people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Clergymen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh of course all 
those - type of people are dying - dying out or - or practically died out. I was just trying to think - well - this house over here used to be a doctor's house, well that - that would come under - under that heading I would say. The doctor's, well that's 
- what I would call the - better class people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What about people like schoolteachers, would that come into that category?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well it's quite possible.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How about things like landlords of pubs and shopkeepers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - well I wouldn't like to say really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Where do you think your father fitted into this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Pardon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Where do you think your fitted into this, would he be a member of the better class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - oh hardly I shouldn't think. Of course he - you - I mean Buckfast and - s
ee some of the big houses there now, well that would be - people like - better class people what I would say better class people. People with here - here - here retired you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 An awful lot of people have retired to this part of the world haven't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
Yes. Of course just this side of Buckfastleigh there's quite a number of - Lords houses and estates and all. See there's Harpmoor House and there's New Park and Hall Court. Well then - well those - type of places like that well - of course all th
e better - class people used to live in these places. Of course then the Hamblyn brothers there was - Rutherford and there was - Bossell, there was Hampstead, that's where the - Hamblyns used to live. Mr James at Bossell, Mr Joe at - Rutherford, Mr Will a
t Hampstead.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did they make many appearances around the town, did they sort of attend functions, things like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 I believe so.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What about the farmers, would you have much contact with the farmers around the area?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh my father did have. Outside Buckfastleigh.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Where would they fit into the scheme of things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
Well they were - well of course the farmers were no doubt Conservatives. My father he'd used to - meet up with 'em through - being clerk of Buckfastleigh West.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 That was after the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well before the first world war. Oh and after. 'Til 1930.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 It was after the first world war he became a member of the council?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Can you remember being brought up to treat people of one sort differently from people of another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well no - no, I always treat people the same. Don't matter who it is.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You weren't ever taught to curtsey or touch your cap?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh yes, that's - that's something we were always told to do. I generally do now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would this be a sign of respect?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Or just a sign of greeting?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - well both if you like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Who would you have to touch your cap to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - I was - I was going to say almost anybody who - especially on the - lady's side.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Wh
o would you say belonged to the same group as yourselves in those days? You said Buckfastleigh was a Liberal town, and the better class would tend to be Conservative, who were all the Liberals then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well the - more the working class - people.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Who would that include?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well all - say - factory workers and perhaps - shop assistants and the like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Who were considered the most important people in Buckfastleigh? Obviously the Hamblyns would be somebody most important, who else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - sha
ll I say the local clergy. Or perhaps - well I was going to - say the Abbey but - of course they were mostly foreign in those days, the Abbey people but it's nearly all English now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Is that the monks?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What about farmers, were they considered very important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes? I should think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
Were there many other employers apart from the Hamblyns? I get the impression Buckfastleigh was virtually a one industry town? Were there any other employers around?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh yes, there are - there was - Berry's of Buckfast.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What did they do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
Oh they used to make blankets, that's Lower Mills. Then Hamblyns used to have a - a small factory up - Higher Buckfast. Well then there's paper - there was the paper mills.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Who owned that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh used to be Regent Smith, of Exeter in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did he live round here or did he just have the firm and live in Exeter?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh he lived in - they lived in Exeter. Oh then - of course there was the farming industry. I just can't think of quarries.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was there much quarrying done in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh not - not in the early days I don't think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 They were building the roads about this time weren't they, did you ever have many sort of labourers come down from the different parts?

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh 
- this road here was - cut in 1926. If I remember rightly they - had a lot of - had a lot of local labour. It was an outside firm that - did it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did they build any roads before the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh af - after the first war I would say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 So you can't remember any say Welshmen or Irishmen coming down to work the roads?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No, I -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Were there many strangers around in those days, or did everybody know everybody else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - more a question of everybody knew everybody else. The onl
y - the only - thing that we'd have in those days - was a - up Hamblyns see or they'd get a - they had a designer here, well he - he came from away, Mr Ridgway well then they - they might get a - used to get somebody down from Yorkshire now and again, a -
 foreman spinner or foreman weaver, used to - very often used to come from Yorkshire.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 They were the skilled people though were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes, might have been.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 But by and large it was sort of local labour and local people that you knew? It was a 
local small community so you'd know if anybody strange came in wouldn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes, rather.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What about people like gypsies, were they ever in evidence?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well we used to get 'em about those days you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What was the general attitude towards gypsies?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - oh goodness knows now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did people like them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh difficult to say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You can't remember any sort of particular instances?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No. Afraid I can't.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did your mother and father have the same attitude to people in different groups? Did they sort of treat everybody the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh I think they did. I think they treated everybody the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What sort of people would you say went to church in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - well - I was going to say - a good many of t
he - better type people, of course Hamblyns we - used - oh and then there was - lot of - better class people here, that I could mention who are - passed on now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would it be mainly the better class people who went to church rather than chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - I should think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Who went to the chapel then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
Well the more - well shall I put it this way, the more - Liberal minded people. For instance you - you compare Church of England for example most of the people - there are conservative minded 
but people like the Wesleyans and the - the Congregational they're more liberal minded.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did your father ever go to chapel or was he always church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh nearly always church. I know we - we used to go to chapel now and again when we were - very sma
ll children. I remember going to Wesleyan chapel once or twice. Congregational. I got recollections of that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Were most of your father's friends church or both?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - well I don't think he'd - don't think he had any particular choice like, who he mixed with.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was there anyone you used to have to call sir or master or madam in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - well people like the - the Hamblyns for instance. I - I -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You used to call them sir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes. Or - I do now if - if I was to meet anybody - more superior like. And - that if somebody I don't know - who I stood with like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Do you remember anyone doing the same thing to your parents? Did anyone call your parents sir or master or madam?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well they might have done but - I can't remember it now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you ever come into much contact with the Hamblyns? Or did your father come into much contact with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh he used to see them every day. Being in - in the office.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would they actually work in the mill, they wouldn't just sort of live outside and own it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You hear stories of some people who own a business but don't actually do much to it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh yes, the - the Hamblyns always used to be there - well my father - was under Mr Will really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How did you find Mr Hamblyn, did you get on ok with him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
Oh got on all right with him, yes. Well talking about - religion well Mr Will was a - non-conformist, but Mr Joe was a Church of England. I don't know what Mr - James was but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 It wasn't all sort of Church of England then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
Amongst the Liberals did all the working class or the Liberals have the same standard of living do you think, or were there some that were better off or poorer than others
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh well that's - that's difficult to say really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Do you remember at this time thinking that your parents had a struggle to make ends meet with four or five children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh well that's - that's a possibility.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you ever sort of consciously realise it do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes. Of course - I believe people were a great deal lower paid in those days what they are now you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was there anybody who was regarded as rough in the area? Not just poor but rough?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well I - that's difficult to say, I can't single out anybody at all.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 There wasn't sort of any incidents of sort of broken homes and things because of it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - I never - don't remember hearing of any.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was there much drunkenness in those parts?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - that I - that I couldn't say really. Probably - you 
got some information about that from Fred Oxenham. He would have - told you a few things in that way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 But you can't remember anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 So you don't think there was a sort of a distinction made between some families who were though to as
 rough and some who were thought of as respectable?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Beg Pardon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You don't remember there being any distinction?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No. No I don't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Do you remember there being any distinction between people who were craftsmen and people who were just lab
ourers? Was there any sort of class distinction between those two groups?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well I - that I can't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was it possible to move from one group into another at this time, sort of work your way up the ladder? Do you remember anything like that?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No, I - I just couldn't say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Can you remember anyone being described as a real gentleman or a real lady?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh that I - I can't single out anybody now really, not - not knowing people so well then as I do now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Do you think your mother sa
w herself as belonging to a particular sort of social group you think she sort of felt she was part of the Liberals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well that - that I couldn't say really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 She never really talked about things like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Do you remember seeing a policeman around?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What was he like?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh we had - we had some fairly good ones and some fairly strict ones, if I remember rightly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What were the strict ones?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well, you - they used to live over Station Road here. That
 - that used to be one of the police houses there on - well I remember one chap, he was called Clarke, PC Clarke, well he - he was very strict. If you weren't behaving yourself when he come out he'd just give you a swipe with his cane, you know, he was on
e of these type of chaps.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 He had a cane did he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh yes, he had a - stick of some sort.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Any other things that happened do you remember? What were the good ones?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well I can't say so much about the good ones as round there, not until - oh
 about 1923. There was one here called - Blackburn, I got on very well with him. Of course I - I do today with him, the police.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was there any sort of occasion if when you were naughty your mother would say I'll call a policeman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Do you think the policemen were OK in regards to the ordinary people? Where did they come from the policemen, were they local people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No. No, they weren't local people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Do you think people like them or got on with them OK?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well I think they did in the long run.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was there much goings on around that time, any crime or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 I can't remember anything.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 There were no sort of big incidents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was your home rented, you say it was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Beg pardon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Your home was rented wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Who was the landlord?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh, the factory.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 The Hamblyns?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did he come round in person to collect the rent?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh no - in a case of - in the place - case of the employees that lived in Bossell Terrace 
I think they - got it taken out of their salary, I'm not quite sure.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 So in fact that's all done in the office?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How did your father get on with him as a landlord, was he a fiar landlord?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - I would think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did he ever do any repairs of anything or come round to inspect the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well I - I don't remember - seeing him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
You say your father wasn't out of work, except by choice, after the first world war when he was doing odds and ends for himself, do you remember your father being ill? Before the first world war.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh yes, he had one - had one bad illness I believe, I - I can't - I can't say what year now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was it before the first war?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Before the first war.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How long was he ill for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well I just don't know, not now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Do you remember whether it was very long?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No, I - I just don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did he ever get help from the Guardians or the Parish or a charity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 I just don't know. And then he had another serious illness in 1926. I remember that one a bit more.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - that must have been nerves or something.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did he find it harder when he was working on his own after 1920 than it was when he was working for a firm?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - I - I don't know, I - I should hardly think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was he able to set up his own affairs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Difficult to say now, so many years ago.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
When there was someone in the district say who the people disapproved of very strongly was there any special way in which they showed it, do you know anything about rough music? Have you ever heard of the phrase?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No recollection of anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 I'd like to ask you one or two questions about work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You left school when you were fourteen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 And went to work with the electricity people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How long did you do that for, a year was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh about eight months.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You say you earnt a shilling a week then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 When you went to the - paper mills?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Paper mill.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What kind of hours would you work there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
Oh - used to be - day work and night work alternately, one week day work from six 'til - Six in the morning to six at night. When it was night work - six at night to eight o'clock the next morning. Well then -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would you have a break in the middle of all that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
Yes. Well then when you finish - when you've been on - night work and finish Saturday morning you - you're off for the weekend until six o'clock Monday morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you work Sundays at all on the paper mill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 So you would work Saturdays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Saturday, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 So it would be a six day week at the paper mill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you have any holidays with pay, either at the electricity job or the mill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 This electricity job, was it a full time job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh no, just - oh it's just - difficult to describe it now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was it a fill in job before you got a full time one?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You were at school when you did this electricity job then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No. Left school altogether.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What were the hours on the electricity job again? Monday to Friday and you had Saturday off?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh no, that was - that was at the paper mill. Electricity - Mondays to Saturday at lunch time I believe.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You wouldn't start work 'til nine o'clock at the electricity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh half past seven. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You say you were paid a shilling a week for the electricity, what about the paper mills job, what were you paid for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh seven and six a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you feel that was a fair wage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh fair wage at that time I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How did that compare say with somebody working in the wool mill down the road?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well, I just don't know that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You say you gave the money to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What was that spent on, your keep?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 And you'd be given pocket money out of that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How did you get on with the other people you worked with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh I got on all right.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You say you worked with that chap Charlie?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Shaw, oh he was at the electricity station. But I got on all right in the paper mill.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Were there many people working at the paper mill, was it a small place or what?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well it was one of - one of three factories they've had. Yes, I got on all right down there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How did you find your employers, both at the electricity and the paper mills, did you find they were OK?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
Well I think the - paper mill was better of the two. Of course the - manager down there was - he was - he and his - family were friends of ours like. As well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did the manager of the paper mills live round the same areas as you then, the same district of Buckfastleigh?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh yes, he lived in - lived in one of the cottages, it was above the factory.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How did your father and mother know him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well through going to church I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Whose Idea was it for you to work in the paper mills, was it your father's or did this man suggest it or what?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well mother's - mother's idea - might have been.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was there anything else you wanted to do do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Had you anything in mind yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well I was always advised - to better myself if I could - of course that's reason of my going to Taunton.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did your father went you to do clerical work? Because he was in clerical work himself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - yes I think because - I was never cut out for heavy work like, what they call manual work.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was it very heavy work in the paper mills or was it light work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - not all that heavy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What did your brothers and sisters do at this time? Some of them would still be at school when you first started work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
Yes, my - well my - my second brother - was a - he used to work in a grocer's shop. And my younger sister and - youngest brother, well they were still going to school then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What did they do eventually?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh my - my youngest brother went to Torquay. He managed to get in with the - Torquay Co-operative electricity department.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 So that was his first job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes. Oh no, I don't think it was his first job but
 he - he got in there eventually. My sister - younger sister, she - went into a job in the pattern room, in the fact - at the factory. Pattern room.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 And that was at the family mill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You say you went to Taunton, you saw this advertised?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh no, I - I don't know how it came about now. I forget how it came about.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 But the idea was you wanted to do something?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh sort of better myself. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 I suppose it would be a big step, leaving home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - I think it was at that time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you know anybody when you went up to Tuanton?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 I suppose you made contacts up there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes, I went up for an interview originally.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 This would be during the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You did this job in Taunton for three years?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How did you find the wages there, were they better than at the paper mills?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well they were better but - it still wasn't - well what I was going to say it wasn't - quite good enough but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What was the employer like?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - had some very happy times there but - of course the money wasn't -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you send any money back home to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh no, I had to - had to pay lodgings and - keep myself you see, as well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How did you feel about your employer, did you get on all right with him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh yes, but - he let me down in the end.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Why was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
Well - I don't know what brought it about now. Although he - he gave me a good reference and - he put it that it was through the - his employees coming back from the war.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 This was 1919 you say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
What did you do when you first came back to Buckfastleigh, did you get a job straight away or was there a period of time between coming back and starting work at the Post Office?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
Oh - I was home from Taunton from - from February until - late October, then I - I got a job up - up Dudley near Birmingham. But that was advertised. Of course I did much better up there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was the money better up there?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What was the difference like between employers in the West Country and Midlands?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
Well - well you - oh - they were a good firm to work for but of course you had to - shall I put it this way, you had to behave - behave yourself up there. You know, there's always director's float - floating around to see what was going on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What kind of house was it, was it wool again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh woollens. Shirts.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did the fact that you came from a wool town sort of put you in good stead when you applied for the job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 It may have done.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did your father have anything to say about you going up to the Midlands, did he want you to go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well I think he did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 I suppose they'd used to the idea of you children moving away because your sister was in London at this time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What kind of hours was the job in Taunton?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Taunton, nine 'til five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How many days a week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Five days - Saturdays nine 'til one I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 So that was better hours really?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What about the Midlands job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh Midlands - eight o'clock 'til six I believe. And Saturdays eight o'clock until - one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 But the wages were better?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Then you came back how long were you in the Midlands for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - 'til the end of September, 1920.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 So you were only up there for a short time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - just over twelve months.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What made you come back then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh slump in trade. So they got rid of a lot of them. I wasn't the only one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Were you sending money home when you were in the Midlands?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No. Keep myself, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Then you came back to live at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 That's when you took up the job with the Post Office?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh I - started in the Post Office - tail end of 1922 I think, that's when I -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 So what did you do in the two years between?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well not very much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was there no work at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No. Of course - unemployment - pay was available then, unemployment benefit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How did you get the job with the Post Office? Was it clerical work the first time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh no. Outdoors it was. Outdoor work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did a postman leave or die or it became vacant or did you sort start off doing something else then work up to being a postman or what?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 When you went to the Post Office did you straight away go on the outdoor deliveries?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - no, not - not actually. I should do - do what I was wanting. Well then eventually I got on the staff.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What kind of hours would you have to work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - all depends what district you were working. See some jobs were part time and other - other jobs were full time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You started off part time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Part time, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How long did it take before you were full time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - well I used to do all the holiday duties for them, that take about - two or three months. W
ell then it wasn't 'til - 1926 that I - began to of on there a bit more regular.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 So what kind of hours would it be part time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh about - oh it - it varied about, say about - just round six 'til - perhaps half past nine, ten o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You say after you took up full time you do that 'til about 1934?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes, beginning of 1935 well then I - I worked for the council part time from - 1934 to 35 and then I went on there full time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You stayed there till 1947?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 1947, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Then you went back to the Post Office?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What were the hours like at the council, were they different again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - nine o'clock 'til - five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would you have Saturdays to work as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Saturday morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Til one o'clock time?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 About one, yes, twelve to - no, nine to twelve I believe.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 When you were doing the postman's job full time that was from about six o'clock 'til one o'clock was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No, was six o'clock 'til about - half past eight, quarter to nine, well then used to go again midday and then again in the afternoon.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 So it was split?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Split into different periods.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 And that would be six days a week would it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well half day Saturdays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 So what would that work out at, about seven hours a day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes. On the average, seven hours a day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What kind of pay did you get for the postal jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
Oh quite good. I had a certificate when I retired and in - in - in that certificate it said that mustn't divulge too much information about the Post Office. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you ever serve any apprenticeship or training period for any of your jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Were you ever a member of any trade union or professional organisation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - member of the Post Office Union - when I joined of course I was asked - when I joined the Post Office.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What about before the first world war, were you a member of anything to do with the mill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you think that employers and workers had the same interests or were they different interests, in the period before the first world war?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh difficult to say really.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did the employers help show you how to do things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well my - my first employer didn't show me very much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What about the one at the paper mill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - yes, things were better in there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you have holidays with pay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 I had holidays when I was in the paper mill but - whether it was with pay or not I don't remember now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What about Bank Holidays, do you remember whether you had Bank Holidays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes. But not Good Fridays. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you get holidays at Taunton?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Holidays with pay, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How many holidays a year would you get?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - had a fortnight's - annual leave and - the Bank Holiday weekends.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you ever think there was a division of interest amongst workers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Like a division between trained craftsmen and other workers, were there any sort of skilled craftsmen in the mill, the paper mill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - up to a point I would say yes. From - the machine man well - he
 had to know his job. And of course the - someone else I'm thinking of - what he used to - grind in the pulp and - put it in the - put it in what they call bin with a great big - great big - tubs. Well that was a - craftsman's job in its way I mean to say
, I always remember - when they get the sort of tarred paper - the - the man in charge of the - beater room, he - bring the sample down and put it in the - drier just to dry it off see what it's like. I remember seeing that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 How did you get on with the
se people, did they ever talk to you very much or show you how it was done, or did they keep themselves to themselves?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - no, not - only - I was only shown - things by the - chap that I worked under.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 When you were working in the office in Taunton do you remember any - what kind of office was it? That was a wool place as well wasn't it?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well it - it was a warehouse.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 In Taunton?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes. It was a ware - that was a warehouse.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 I thought the Midlands was a warehouse?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes, that was, Taunton was too, a small one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 But you were in the office in Taunton?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes, and - I used to work in the warehouse as well. Help with the orders.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was there any division there between the office workers and the sort of general labourers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh - well, there wasn't very many working in this particular place, only about - two, three - about eight or nine, that's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What was the warehouse for? Was it a woollen warehouse?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Woollen warehouse, not the - it's - it was an - a wh
olesale warehouse see, used to buy from the - from the factories and sell to the - the shops, tailors shops and drapers shops.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Do you think that full time work changed your attitude to life in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh I don't know, hardly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Nothing chang
ed in the way of your actual attitude to life, it obviously changed in the way of having to get up early and things like that? But nothing sort of dramatic changed for you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh I don't know hardly. Don't think I've taken any - all that notice of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 You continued to live at home after you left school 'til you were in 1916, so you'd be twenty-one then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes. Yes, oh I was in Taunton then. Saw my twenty-first birthday in Taunton.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did anyone come up for it or did you go home?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you spend Sundays any differently when you left school, did you go to Sunday school twice a day still?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 I did until I - until I left home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you carry on going to church when you were in Taunton? You did because you went bell ringing didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes. Of course I still used to - spend my Sundays as I did at home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would you go to Sunday school in Taunton?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No. Well no, not Sunday school. Not - not then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 When did you stop Sunday school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh when I went away from home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
Did starting full time work have any effect on your relationship with your parents? Did they treat you more as an adult once you started working?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh I think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would they talk to you more about their sort of adult life once you'd left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No, they - of course when I was away from home - we always used to write to each other and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
What about your brothers and sisters, especially the younger ones, when you left school, would they sort of think of you as something a bit sort of different from them because they were still at school and you'd left?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh, I don't know hardly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you take any interest in politics at all during this time before the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - not all that interest, not in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Were you Liberal the same as your mother and father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Why do you think you were Liberal, because your mother and father were Liberal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh no, it was - I always was - Liberal minded.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What do you think being Liberal minded means, involves?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - well sort of - I was going to say, it feels like - sort of - happy go between. If I can put it that way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Go between between what?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well happy medium should we say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 So you're sort of moderate and tolerant you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you ever vote in a general election before 1919?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Were you ever a member of any political party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No. Well - only in late years. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 So you wouldn't work for any of the parties at an election for instance?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you take part in any political activity other than at election time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Not in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 
You told me earlier something of how you spent your spare time, playing with the neighbours and - going to things like fairs and the odd theatre 
and circus and going for walks and picking violets and things, did anything happen once you'd left school would you do anything different then? Or would it be much the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - see, when you go away from the country, or you - can't very well go -
 when you get into the town you can't very well go - for instance picking flowers. Well what I used to do is to go for long walks - trying to sort of explore a bit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Was this when you moved to Taunton?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 What about before you went to Tau
nton, did you do anything different between leaving school and when you were working, was there any difference in your way of life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No. No, no, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you make any new friends at that time when you left school and went to work? Or
 would you sort of keep with the friends you had, the neighbours and school friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well only - I mixed a bit more you know. As I grew older I mixed a bit more with the - some of the younger fellows round about.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would they be people from work or people from school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh people I remembered from school and - and those who used to go - school with my brothers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 I suppose you'd go around with your brothers still because they wouldn't be a lot younger than you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did girls tend to go with themselves and boys with themselves in those days, would you play with your sisters after you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Oh no - we used to keep our own company then. As you grew older.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you go out much in the evenings when you were at work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - sometimes I used to go out but it depends what - how near it was and - what was doing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 It was mainly sort of making your own amusements I suppose?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Yes, rather.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you have any special friends at this time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you ever bring friends home after you left school? Did you ever bring anyone back from work say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 I don't think so, I - I don't quite remember.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Would your parents meet your friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well they used to know who we - who we mixed up with.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Because I suppose in a small village everyone's in the same area, they all know everybody else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Mm. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did they expect to know where you were when you went out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - if we went out and - we came back any like late they - they'd want to know where we'd been.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Did you have to be home by a certain time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well they - liked us - liked us to be in - reasonably early.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9466542 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Why was that, because of the dark or what?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1856064 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8934728\charrsid7931254 Well - habit more than anything else I suppose.
\par }}